sourcesContent: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { filter, tap } from 'rxjs'; import { UserServiceService } from 'src/app/user-service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-add-cla', templateUrl: './add-cla.component.html', styleUrls: ['./add-cla.component.css'] }) export class AddClaComponent implements OnInit { ngOnInit(): void { this.showteacher(); console.log(this.data); } constructor(private teacher:UserServiceService){} data:any[]=[] showteacher(){ this.teacher.getTeacher().subscribe((student)=>this.data=student) console.log(this.data); } }
